spec_data.Name: python2-paste-deploy
spec_data.Description:
This tool provides code to load WSGI applications and servers from
URIs; these URIs can refer to Python Eggs for INI-style configuration
files.  PasteScript provides commands to serve applications based on
this configuration file.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:49:42 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Load, configure, and compose WSGI applications and servers
